==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gibraltar
<hw>Gi*bral"tar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
strongly fortified town on the south coast of Spain, held by the British
since 1704; hence, an impregnable stronghold.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of candy sweetmeat, or a piece of it; --
called, in full, <altname>Gibraltar rock</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gibstaff</ent>⟦br⟧
